    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><div>It is apparent that we modify any form in drupal by implementing <a href="https://api.drupal.org/api/drupal/modules!system!system.api.php/function/hook_form_alter/7">hook_form_alter()</a>. But there are cases when even the <a href="https://api.drupal.org/api/drupal/modules!system!system.api.php/function/hook_form_alter/7">hook_form_alter()</a> cannot offer a solution in altering the form fields. I recently faced such a situation, when I was trying to empty the labels in the password &amp; confirm password fields in the user registeration form in Drupal 7.</div>
